Package: counter
Type: Package
Title: Modelling and forecasting of count data
Version: 0.1.0.41001
Date: 2018-09-17
Authors@R: person("Ivan", "Svetunkov", email = "ivan@svetunkov.ru", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment="Lecturer at Centre for Marketing Analytics and Forecasting, Lancaster University, UK")
URL: https://github.com/config-i1/counter
BugReports: https://github.com/config-i1/counter/issues
Description: The package contains functions for modelling and forecasting of count
             data. This includes Hurdle Shifted Poisson and dynamic Negative
             Binomial models.
License: GPL (>=3)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports:
    smooth,
    greybox (>= 0.3.1),
    stats,
    graphics,
    utils,
    nloptr
Suggests:
    doMC,
    doParallel,
    foreach,
    testthat,
    rmarkdown,
    knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
